u Vá»±c Xung Quanh</p><p>Khu vá»±c xung quanh ThÃ¡c Niagara cÅ©ng ÄÃ¡ng Äá» khÃ¡m phÃ¡. CÃ´ng viÃªn Niagara Falls, vá»i nhá»¯ng khu vá»±c xanh mÃ¡t vÃ  cÃ¡c con ÄÆ°á»ng Äi bá» Äáº¹p, lÃ  nÆ¡i lÃ½ tÆ°á»ng Äá» thÆ° giÃ£n sau khi ngáº¯m thÃ¡c. Báº¡n cÅ©ng cÃ³ thá» ghÃ© thÄm cÃ¡c Äiá»m du lá»ch ná»i báº­t khÃ¡c nhÆ° Báº£o tÃ ng vÃ  Trung tÃ¢m Du lá»ch Niagara, nÆ¡i cung cáº¥p nhiá»u thÃ´ng tin thÃº vá» vá» lá»ch sá»­ vÃ  Äá»a lÃ½ cá»§a thÃ¡c.</p><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/Bai_Viet/niagara-1459676.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"></p><p> </p><p>5. Ghi Láº¡i Nhá»¯ng Khoáº£nh Kháº¯c Äáº·c Biá»t</p><p>Cuá»i cÃ¹ng, Äá»«ng quÃªn mang theo mÃ¡y áº£nh Äá» ghi láº¡i nhá»¯ng khoáº£nh kháº¯c Äáº¹p nháº¥t cá»§a chuyáº¿n thÄm. Cáº£nh quan tuyá»t Äáº¹p cá»§a ThÃ¡c Niagara, vá»i nhá»¯ng mÃ u sáº¯c vÃ  Ã¡nh sÃ¡ng biáº¿n Äá»i, lÃ  má»t cÆ¡ há»i tuyá»t vá»i Äá» cÃ³ nhá»¯ng bá»©c áº£nh áº¥n tÆ°á»£ng vÃ  lÆ°u giá»¯ ká»· niá»m ÄÃ¡ng nhá».</p><p> </p><p><em>ThÃ¡c Niagara khÃ´ng chá» lÃ  má»t ká»³ quan thiÃªn nhiÃªn ná»i báº­t mÃ  cÃ²n lÃ  má»t tráº£i nghiá»m tuyá»t vá»i dÃ nh cho táº¥t cáº£ nhá»¯ng ai yÃªu thÃ­ch váº» Äáº¹p hoang sÆ¡ cá»§a thiÃªn nhiÃªn. Vá»i sá»± hÃ¹ng vÄ©, cÃ¡c gÃ³c nhÃ¬n Äa dáº¡ng, vÃ  nhá»¯ng tráº£i nghiá»m Äáº§y cáº£m xÃºc, ThÃ¡c Niagara cháº¯c cháº¯n sáº½ Äá» láº¡i áº¥n tÆ°á»£ng sÃ¢u sáº¯c trong lÃ²ng báº¡n. Náº¿u báº¡n cÃ³ cÆ¡ há»i, hÃ£y dÃ nh thá»i gian Äá» táº­n hÆ°á»ng váº» Äáº¹p tuyá»t vá»i vÃ  sá»©c máº¡nh cá»§a má»t trong nhá»¯ng thÃ¡c nÆ°á»c ná»i tiáº¿ng nháº¥t tháº¿ giá»i nÃ y.</em></p>','Chiêm Ngưỡng Vẻ Đẹp Tự Nhiên Của Thác Niagara','Nằm trên biên giới giữa Canada và Mỹ, Thác Niagara không chỉ thu hút du khách bởi kích thước khổng lồ và dòng nước cuộn chảy, mà còn bởi cảm giác bối rối và phấn khích mà nó mang lại.','2026-06-05 15:08:38','2026-06-05 15:08:38'),(12,6,'en','Witness the Majestic Beauty of Niagara Falls: A Must-Visit Natural Wonder','witness-the-majestic-beauty-of-niagara-falls-a-must-visit-natural-wonder','When it comes to world-renowned natural wonders, Niagara Falls undoubtedly tops the bucket list. Blessed with a mystical charm and breathtaking power, this iconic destination never fails to leave travelers in awe.','<h3><b>1. First Impressions: The Roaring Grandeur of Niagara Falls</b></h3><p>The moment you step foot near Niagara Falls, its sheer scale and grandeur will take your breath away. The site is comprised of three distinct waterfalls: <b>Horseshoe Falls</b>, <b>American Falls</b>, and <b>Bridal Veil Falls</b>.</p><p>Among them, Horseshoe Fallsâlocated on the Canadian sideâis the largest and most spectacular, stretching 670 meters wide and plunging about 53 meters down. The way the sunlight dances on the rushing water, combined with the thunderous roar of the falls, creates a hypnotic spectacle you simply cannot look away from.</p><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/Bai_Viet/niagara-3993912.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"></p><p> </p><h3><b>2. Best Ways to Experience the Falls From Every Angle</b></h3><p>To truly appreciate the magnificence of Niagara Falls, you need to witness it from multiple perspectives. Whether you prefer a bird\'s-eye view or getting up close and personal, here are the best ways to explore:</p><ul><li><p><b>Skylon Tower Observation Deck:</b> Located just a few kilometers away, the Skylon Tower offers a stunning panoramic view of the entire falls and the surrounding cityscape. You can even enjoy a world-class meal at its revolving restaurant while taking in the breathtaking scenery from 236 meters in the air.</p></li></ul><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/Bai_Viet/dd07bd47fb31918ad5fb037a71fb5e960465c0b2.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"></p><p><br></p><ul><li><p><b>The Hornblower Cruise Experience:</b> A definitive must-do is boarding the famous Hornblower cruise (now Niagara City Cruises). This boat tour takes you right into the heart of the mist. You will feel the raw, immense power of the crashing water and likely get a bit soakedâbut that only adds to the thrill of the adventure!</p></li></ul><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/Bai_Viet/boat-1834837.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"></p><p><br></p><ul><li><p><b>Strolling Along the Brink of the Falls:</b> Built right along the edge of Horseshoe Falls, the misty walking paths offer an intimate, detailed view of the cascading waters. Standing just feet away from the crest, you can literally feel the vibration of every crashing wave.</p></li></ul><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/Bai_Viet/niagara-1590345.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"></p><p> </p><h3><b>3. Niagara Falls at Night: A Magical Light Show</b></h3><p>Niagara Falls doesn\'t sleep when the sun goes down; instead, it transforms into a glowing, mystical wonderland. Every evening, the falls are illuminated in a vibrant spectrum of colors, creating a mesmerizing and magical display. You can admire this breathtaking light show from nearby viewpoints or join a night tour to experience the enchanting ambiance of the falls under the starry sky.</p><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/Bai_Viet/Niagara_Falls_Night.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"></p><p> </p><h3><b>4. Exploring the Vibrant Surrounding Area</b></h3><p>The excitement doesn\'t stop at the waterfalls. The surrounding <b>Niagara Parks</b> area is packed with lush green spaces and scenic walking trails, making it the perfect spot to unwind after your sightseeing tour. Don\'t forget to check out nearby attractions, including local museums and visitor centers, to uncover fascinating insights into the rich history and geology of the falls.</p><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/Bai_Viet/niagara-1459676.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"></p><p> </p><h3><b>5. Capture Your Unforgettable Memories</b></h3><p>Last but not least, make sure your camera or smartphone is fully charged! The ever-changing light, rainbows, and dramatic landscapes of Niagara Falls provide the ultimate backdrop for Instagram-worthy photos and lifelong memories.</p><h3><b>Conclusion</b></h3><p>Niagara Falls is more than just a famous landmark; it is an exhilarating journey for anyone who loves the raw, untamed beauty of nature. With its roaring grandeur, diverse vantage points, and emotional thrill, this natural wonder is guaranteed to leave a lasting impression on your heart. If you ever get the chance, pack your bags and go experience the awe-inspiring power of one of the world\'s most famous waterfalls!</p>','Witness the Majestic Beauty of Niagara Falls: A Must-Visit Natural Wonder','Straddling the border between Canada and the United States, Niagara Falls captivates millions of visitors not just with its massive scale and roaring waters, but also with the pure thrill and excitement it brings.','2026-06-05 15:08:38','2026-06-05 15:08:38'),(13,7,'vi','Đi Chơi Mộc Châu Mùa Hoa Nở - Trải Nghiệm Tuyệt Đẹp Giữa Cao Nguyên','i-choi-moc-chau-mua-hoa-no-trai-nghiem-tuyet-ep-giua-cao-nguyen','Mộc Châu, cao nguyên xanh mát nằm ở tỉnh Sơn La, là một trong những điểm du lịch nổi tiếng nhất miền Bắc Việt Nam.','<p>Má»i mÃ¹a trong nÄm, Má»c ChÃ¢u láº¡i khoÃ¡c lÃªn mÃ¬nh má»t váº» Äáº¹p riÃªng, tá»« sáº¯c tráº¯ng tinh khÃ´i cá»§a hoa cáº£i, hoa máº­n Äáº¿n sáº¯c vÃ ng rá»±c rá»¡ cá»§a hoa dÃ£ quá»³. HÃ£y cÃ¹ng khÃ¡m phÃ¡ váº» Äáº¹p cá»§a Má»c ChÃ¢u qua tá»«ng mÃ¹a hoa ná»!</p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/2038129_f83304bf14cf9f207102d3ad0a79ef02.png\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>Nguá»n: Baoquangninh</p><h3> </h3><h3>1. MÃ¹a Hoa Máº­n (ThÃ¡ng 1 - ThÃ¡ng 2)</h3><p>Khi xuÃ¢n vá», Má»c ChÃ¢u khoÃ¡c lÃªn mÃ¬nh táº¥m Ã¡o tráº¯ng tinh khÃ´i cá»§a hoa máº­n. Nhá»¯ng vÆ°á»n hoa máº­n ná» rá», tráº£i dÃ i kháº¯p cÃ¡c sÆ°á»n Äá»i, táº¡o nÃªn cáº£m giÃ¡c nhÆ° láº¡c vÃ o chá»n bá»ng lai tiÃªn cáº£nh. Hoa 