-06-05 15:10:58','2026-06-05 15:10:58'),(14,7,'en','Visiting Moc Chau During the Flower Season - A Breathtaking Experience on the Plateau','i-choi-moc-chau-mua-hoa-no-trai-nghiem-tuyet-ep-giua-cao-nguyen','Moc Chau, a cool green plateau in Son La Province, is one of the most famous tourist destinations in Northern Vietnam.','<p>Each season, Moc Chau dons a unique beauty, from the pristine white of mustard flowers and plum blossoms to the radiant yellow of wild sunflowers. Letâs explore the beauty of Moc Chau through its blooming seasons!</p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/2038129_f83304bf14cf9f207102d3ad0a79ef02.png\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>Source: Baoquangninh</p><h3> </h3><h3>1. Plum Blossom Season (January - February)</h3><p>When spring arrives, Moc Chau is adorned with the pure white of plum blossoms. The plum orchards bloom, stretching across the hillsides, creating a fairy-tale-like scenery. Plum blossoms not only symbolize purity but also represent new beginnings. Visitors can stroll under the plum trees, admire the beautiful scenery, and enjoy the cool spring air.</p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/MocChau/hoaman.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>Source: Mia.vn</p><p> </p><h3>2. Ban Flower Season (March - April)</h3><p>The Ban flower, a symbol of the Northwest, blooms in spring, covering the forests and roadsides with its pure white petals. The white Ban flowers blend with the green of the mountains, creating a stunning natural painting. Ban flowers are not only beautiful but also carry deep cultural significance for the Thai ethnic people. Visitors can stop by the Ban flower roads to take photos and enjoy the pristine beauty of these flowers.</p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/MocChau/hoaban-new.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>Source: vnexpress.net</p><p> </p><h3>3. Mustard Flower Season (October - December)</h3><p>In late autumn and early winter, Moc Chau transforms into a \"white paradise\" with endless fields of mustard flowers. The white mustard flowers bloom, covering the valleys and hillsides, creating a romantic and poetic scene. This is the perfect time for visitors to immerse themselves in nature, take check-in photos, and enjoy the fresh air.</p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/MocChau/hoacai.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>Source: Mia.vn</p><p> </p><h3>4. Wild Sunflower Season (November)</h3><p>In late autumn, Moc Chau is painted with the radiant yellow of wild sunflowers. The roads leading to Moc Chau are filled with the golden hues of wild sunflowers, creating a wild and vibrant scenery. Wild sunflowers bloom along the hillsides, roadsides, and valleys, bringing warmth to the cool weather. This is the perfect time for visitors to explore the wild beauty of the plateau.</p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/MocChau/hoadaquy-new.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>Source: mia.vn</p><p> </p><h3>5. Other Must-Visit Destinations</h3><p>In addition to the vibrant flower seasons, Moc Chau has many other attractive destinations, such as:</p><ul><li><p>Heart-Shaped Tea Hills: Lush green tea hills trimmed into unique heart shapes, attracting visitors for photography and enjoying fragrant tea.</p></li><li><p>Ban Ang â Crystal Clear Lake: A peaceful destination with a clear blue lake surrounded by green pine hills.</p></li><li><p>Dai Yem Waterfall: A majestic waterfall with water cascading from above, creating an impressive natural scene.</p></li></ul><h3>Conclusion</h3><p>Moc Chau during the flower season is a breathtaking natural painting, offering unforgettable experiences for visitors. Whether itâs the pristine white of mustard flowers, plum blossoms, Ban flowers, or the radiant yellow of wild sunflowers, Moc Chau never fails to captivate. Plan your trip to Moc Chau and immerse yourself in the beauty of nature and fresh air!</p>','Visiting Moc Chau During the Flower Season - A Breathtaking Experience on the Plateau','With its year-round cool climate, picturesque landscapes, and especially the vibrant flower seasons, Moc Chau becomes an ideal destination for nature lovers and those seeking peace.','2026-06-05 15:10:58','2026-06-05 15:10:58'),(15,8,'vi','Du Lịch Hiện Đại – Không Chỉ Để Đi, Mà Để Sống Thật','du-lich-hien-ai-khong-chi-e-i-ma-e-song-that','Du lịch hiện đại đang trở thành xu hướng mới – nơi mỗi chuyến đi không chỉ để “đi”, mà để sống chậm lại, sâu sắc hơn, bền vững hơn và cá nhân hoá hơn.','<h2>Du Lá»ch Hiá»n Äáº¡i LÃ  GÃ¬?</h2><p> </p><p>Trong bá»i cáº£nh tháº¿ giá»i ngÃ y cÃ ng thay Äá»i, cÃ¡ch con ngÆ°á»i khÃ¡m phÃ¡ cÅ©ng dáº§n thay Äá»i. Nhá»¯ng tour du lá»ch dÃ y Äáº·c, cháº¡y Äua Äiá»m Äáº¿n ÄÃ£ dáº§n nhÆ°á»ng chá» cho nhá»¯ng chuyáº¿n Äi nháº¹ nhÃ ng, tinh gá»n nhÆ°ng Äáº­m cháº¥t tráº£i nghiá»m.</p><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/Tips/1-smartvel.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p><p> </p><p> </p><h3>1. CÃ¡ nhÃ¢n hoÃ¡ tráº£i nghiá»m â HÃ nh trÃ¬nh theo cÃ¡ch cá»§a báº¡n</h3><p> </p><p>Thay vÃ¬ nhá»¯ng lá»ch trÃ¬nh ráº­p khuÃ´n, du lá»ch hiá»n Äáº¡i hÆ°á»ng Äáº¿n sá»± linh hoáº¡t vÃ  riÃªng tÆ°. Du khÃ¡ch cÃ³ thá» lá»±a chá»n Äiá»m Äáº¿n, tá»c Äá» hÃ nh trÃ¬nh vÃ  hoáº¡t Äá»ng theo sá» thÃ­ch cÃ¡ nhÃ¢n. ÄÃ¢y chÃ­nh lÃ  cÃ¡ch Äá» má»i ngÆ°á»i káº¿t ná»i vá»i chÃ­nh mÃ¬nh khi Äi xa.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><h3>2. Ãt Äiá»m Äáº¿n â nhiá»u cáº£m xÃºc</h3><p> </p><p>KhÃ´ng cáº§n âÄi cho nhiá»uâ, mÃ  lÃ  á» láº¡i Äá»§ lÃ¢u Äá» cáº£m nháº­n. á» láº¡i má»t nÆ¡i vÃ i ngÃ y, trÃ² chuyá»n cÃ¹ng ngÆ°á»i dÃ¢n Äá»a phÆ°Æ¡ng, thá»­ má»t mÃ³n Än báº£n xá»© â ÄÃ³ lÃ  cÃ¡ch Äá» chuyáº¿n Äi thá»±c sá»± Äá»ng láº¡i kÃ½ á»©c.</p><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/Tips/2-forbes.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><h3>3. Sá»ng nhÆ° ngÆ°á»i báº£n Äá»a</h3><p> </