s://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/USA/Chicago/04.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\"></h2><h2> </h2><p> </p><h2>Jazz &amp; Blues â Ãm nháº¡c ÄÆ°á»ng phá» Äáº­m cháº¥t Má»¹</h2><p> </p><p>Chicago lÃ  cÃ¡i nÃ´i cá»§a Jazz vÃ  Blues, hai thá» loáº¡i Ã¢m nháº¡c ÄÃ£ Äá»nh hÃ¬nh vÄn hÃ³a Má»¹. Khi mÃ n ÄÃªm buÃ´ng xuá»ng, tiáº¿ng saxophone vÃ  guitar ngÃ¢n vang tá»« nhá»¯ng quÃ¡n bar nhá» hay sÃ¢n kháº¥u ÄÆ°á»ng phá». GhÃ© vÃ o má»t club lÃ¢u Äá»i, thÆ°á»ng thá»©c má»t ly cocktail vÃ  tháº£ há»n theo tá»«ng giai Äiá»u â ÄÃ³ lÃ  má»t Chicago ráº¥t riÃªng mÃ  báº¡n khÃ³ tÃ¬m tháº¥y á» nÆ¡i khÃ¡c.</p><h2> </h2><h2> </h2><p> </p><p> </p><h2>áº¨m thá»±c Chicago â Äáº­m ÄÃ  vÃ  khÃ³ cÆ°á»¡ng</h2><p> </p><p>áº¨m thá»±c nÆ¡i ÄÃ¢y vá»«a dÃ¢n dÃ£ vá»«a Äá»c ÄÃ¡o. Chicago-style hot dog vá»i xÃºc xÃ­ch thÆ¡m, bÃ¡nh mÃ¬ má»m, phá»§ Äáº§y dÆ°a chua, hÃ nh tÃ¢y vÃ  mÃ¹ táº¡t vÃ ng; hay deep dish pizza dÃ y Ãº á»¥ nhÃ¢n phÃ´ mai, sá»t cÃ  chua vÃ  topping phong phÃº â Äá»u lÃ  nhá»¯ng mÃ³n báº¡n khÃ´ng thá» bá» lá»¡. NgoÃ i ra, thÃ nh phá» cÃ²n cÃ³ nhá»¯ng nhÃ  hÃ ng Michelin danh tiáº¿ng, nÆ¡i há»i tá»¥ tinh hoa áº©m thá»±c quá»c táº¿.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/USA/Chicago/01.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"></p><p> </p><p> </p><p>Chicago khÃ´ng phÃ´ trÆ°Æ¡ng, mÃ  láº·ng láº½ chinh phá»¥c trÃ¡i tim du khÃ¡ch báº±ng sá»± hÃ²a quyá»n giá»¯a cá» Äiá»n vÃ  hiá»n Äáº¡i, giá»¯a nhá»p sá»ng nÄng Äá»ng vÃ  nÃ©t tráº§m máº·c cá»§a lá»ch sá»­. Náº¿u báº¡n muá»n má»t hÃ nh trÃ¬nh vá»«a khÃ¡m phÃ¡ vá»«a thÆ° giÃ£n, Chicago â Vá»nh Mexico â VÃ¹ng Caribbean cháº¯c cháº¯n sáº½ Äá» láº¡i nhá»¯ng ká»· niá»m khÃ³ quÃªn.</p><p> </p><p>LiÃªn há» Travel Plus Äá» ÄÆ°á»£c tÆ° váº¥n lá»ch trÃ¬nh trá»n váº¹n nháº¥t cho chuyáº¿n Äi cá»§a báº¡n.</p>','Du Lịch Chicago – Thành Phố Gió Hút Hồn Giữa Lòng Nước Mỹ','Nhắc đến Chicago, người ta thường gọi đây là “Thành phố gió” – nơi hội tụ vẻ đẹp của kiến trúc hiện đại, lịch sử lâu đời và không khí nghệ thuật độc đáo.','2026-06-05 15:46:51','2026-06-05 15:47:11'),(22,11,'en','Chicago – The Windy City That Steals Hearts in the Heart of America','chicago-the-windy-city-that-steals-hearts-in-the-heart-of-america','When people think of Chicago, they often call it “The Windy City” – a place where modern architecture, rich history, and a distinctive artistic spirit converge.','<p>From the vast shores of Lake Michigan to tree-lined boulevards, every corner tells its own story.</p><h3> </h3><h2>The Bean â Chicagoâs Iconic Photo Spot</h2><p> </p><p>Located in Millennium Park, Cloud Gate â affectionately known as <em>The Bean</em> â is a stainless steel masterpiece with a mirror-like surface reflecting the sky, skyscrapers, and passersby. Visitors can stroll around it or even step inside âthe bellyâ of The Bean to marvel at fascinating reflections. Whether day or night, this is one of the cityâs most dazzling and irresistible check-in spots.</p><h2> </h2><h2><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/USA/Chicago/02.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"></h2><h2> </h2><h2> </h2><h2>Willis Tower â A Sky-High Thrill</h2><p> </p><p>Once the tallest building in the world, Willis Tower remains an iconic part of Chicagoâs skyline. From its 103rd floor, you can step onto the Skydeck â a glass box extending out into open air, perched more than 400 meters above ground. Standing suspended in the sky, with the entire city beneath your feet, will leave you both thrilled and breathless.</p><h2> </h2><h2><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/USA/Chicago/04.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\"></h2><h2> </h2><h2> </h2><h2>Cruising the Chicago River â An Architectural Journey</h2><p> </p><p>The Chicago River splits the city into stunning architectural âpuzzles.â The famous Chicago Architecture River Cruise will glide you along calm green waters, passing over 50 remarkable buildings ranging from early 20th-century gems to bold contemporary designs. Each structure tells a tale of vision, creativity, and the cityâs storied past.</p><h3> </h3><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><h2>Jazz &amp; Blues â Americaâs Musical Soul</h2><p> </p><p>Chicago is the birthplace of Jazz and Blues, two genres that shaped American music culture. When night falls, the sound of saxophones and guitars flows from cozy bars and street stages alike. Step into a historic club, sip a cocktail, and let yourself drift away with the music â this is the Chicago you wonât find anywhere else.</p><h2> </h2><h2> </h2><h2> </h2><h2> </h2><h2>Chicagoâs Culinary Delights â Rich and Irresistible</h2><p> </p><p>The cityâs cuisine is a blend of hearty and unique flavors. Try a Chicago-style hot dog â juicy sausage in a soft bun, topped with pickles, onions, and yellow mustard â or indulge in a deep-dish pizza, thick with gooey cheese, rich tomato sauce, and generous toppings. For fine dining lovers, Chicago also boasts Michelin-starred restaurants showcasing the best of global gastronomy.</p><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/USA/Chicago/01.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"></p><p> </p><p> </p><p>Chicago doesnât boast loudly â it quietly wins hearts with its seamless blend of old and new, of dynamic city life and moments steeped in history. If youâre looking for a journey that combines discovery with relaxation, Chicago â the Gulf of Mexico â the Caribbean will surely leave you with memories to treasure.</p><p> </p><p>Contact Travel Plus for a tailor-made itinerary to make the most of your adventure.</p>','Chicago – The Windy City That Steals Hearts in the Heart of America','When people think of Chicago, they often call it “The Windy City” – a place where modern architecture, rich history, and a distinctive artistic spirit converge.','2026-06-05 15:46:51','2026-06-05 15:47:11'),(23,12,'vi','Trải Nghiệm Mùa Đông Ở Úc – Khác Lạ Mà Đáng Giá!','tra