ul><li><p>TrÃ¡nh nÃ³ng hiá»u quáº£: TrÃ¡i mÃºi giá» vÃ  thá»i tiáº¿t, Ãc lÃ  Äiá»m trá»n náº¯ng lÃ½ tÆ°á»ng trong nhá»¯ng ngÃ y hÃ¨ oi bá»©c.</p></li></ul><p> </p><ul><li><p>Chi phÃ­ tiáº¿t kiá»m hÆ¡n: MÃ¹a ÄÃ´ng lÃ  mÃ¹a tháº¥p Äiá»m du lá»ch táº¡i Ãc â Äá»ng nghÄ©a vá»i vÃ© mÃ¡y bay, dá»ch vá»¥ khÃ¡ch sáº¡n, tourâ¦ cÃ³ má»©c giÃ¡ Æ°u ÄÃ£i hÆ¡n.</p></li></ul><p> </p><ul><li><p>Tráº£i nghiá»m Äá»c ÄÃ¡o, khÃ´ng trÃ¹ng láº·p: Tá»« tuyáº¿t tráº¯ng Äáº¿n lá» há»i Ã¡nh sÃ¡ng, má»i khoáº£nh kháº¯c á» Ãc mÃ¹a ÄÃ´ng Äá»u ÄÃ¡ng giÃ¡.</p></li></ul><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><h2>Äáº·t Tour Du Lá»ch Ãc MÃ¹a ÄÃ´ng Ngay HÃ´m Nay!</h2><p> </p><p>Báº¡n cÃ³ muá»n Ã´m mÃ¹a ÄÃ´ng má»t láº§n trong Äá»i?</p><p><br>Gá»i ngay Äá» nháº­n lá»ch trÃ¬nh chi tiáº¿t vÃ  cÃ¡c Æ°u ÄÃ£i háº¥p dáº«n tá»« Travel Plus!</p>','Trải Nghiệm Mùa Đông Ở Úc – Khác Lạ Mà Đáng Giá!','Khi Việt Nam đang bước vào mùa hè rực lửa, nước Úc lại khoác lên mình chiếc áo đông mát lạnh, nhẹ nhàng và đầy thi vị.','2026-06-05 15:55:58','2026-06-05 15:55:58'),(24,12,'en','Experience Winter in Australia – A Refreshing & Rewarding Escape!','experience-winter-in-australia-a-refreshing-rewarding-escape','While Vietnam is heating up in the height of summer, Australia slips into a cool, tranquil winter coat, offering a gentle and poetic charm.','<h2> </h2><h2>If you\'re looking to escape the heat and discover something truly different this July, a winter getaway to Australia might just be your perfect answer!</h2><p> </p><h2>When Does Winter Start in Australia?</h2><p> </p><p>Unlike Vietnam, winter in Australia begins in June and lasts through August. This is the perfect time to enjoy the signature chill of the Southern Hemisphere, soak in the calm scenery, and take part in unique seasonal activities.</p><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/UC/02/mount.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><h2>Christmas in July â Why Not?</h2><p> </p><p>Have you ever thought about celebrating Christmas in the middle of July? In Australia, itâs the perfect opportunity to cozy up with a hot cocoa and soak in the romantic winter ambiance of the Southern Hemisphere.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><h2>Step Into a Snowy Wonderland</h2><p> </p><p>Feel the thrill of skiing or snowboarding at Mount Buller or Thredbo, the most popular snow resorts in Victoria and New South Wales. Surrounded by white, glistening snow, itâll feel like youâve stepped into a European winter fairytale.</p><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/UC/02/Thredbo.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"></p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><h2>Melbourne â Winterâs Soft Charm</h2><p> </p><p>Melbourne in winter exudes gentle beauty, with its European-inspired streets, warm cafÃ©s, and relaxed locals. Donât miss the Queen Victoria Market Winter Night Market â a foodie\'s paradise and festive playground of lights, music, and vibrant energy.</p><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/UC/02/melbourne.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"></p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><h2>Get Close to Australiaâs Adorable Wildlife</h2><p> </p><p>Winter is also a great time to meet koalas and kangaroos in the fresh, cool air. Visiting nature reserves and wildlife parks will give you an unforgettable look at Australiaâs wild side â up close and charmingly chilly.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><h2>Illuminate Adelaide â A World-Class Light Festival</h2><p> </p><p>Donât miss Illuminate Adelaide â a spectacular festival of light, sound, and art held every July. The entire city lights up with interactive installations, live music, and immersive visual art. Itâs an unmissable event for art and culture lovers!</p><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/UC/02/illuminate_adelaide.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p><p> </p><p> </p><h2>Queen Victoria Winter Night Market â Melbourneâs Heartbeat</h2><p> </p><p>Every Wednesday evening from June to August, Melbourneâs iconic Queen Victoria Market transforms into a winter night wonderland. Think sizzling street food, hot mulled wine, rich hot chocolate, live music, artisan crafts, and cozy vibes. A must-visit for your Aussie winter getaway!</p><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/UC/02/queen_victoria_market.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"></p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><h2>Why Travel to Australia in Winter?</h2><p> </p><p>Escape the heat: Australiaâs reverse seasons make it a perfect destination to cool off during Vietnamâs summer.</p><p><br>Budget-friendly travel: Winter is Australiaâs low season, meaning better deals on flights, accommodation, and tours.</p><p><br>One-of-a-kind experiences: From snowy landscapes to dazzling light festivals, every moment in Australiaâs winter is a memory waiting to be made.</p><h2> </h2><h2> </h2><h2> </h2><h2>Book Your Winter Holiday to Australia Today!</h2><p> </p><p>Ready to experience winter in a whole new way?</p><p><br>Let Travel Plus help you wrap yourself in the magic of an Australian winter.</p>','Experience Winter in Australia – A Refreshing & Rewarding Escape!','While Vietnam is heating up in the height of summer, Australia slips into a cool, tranquil winter coat, offering a gentle and poetic charm.','2026-06-05 15:55:58','2026-06-05 15:55:58'),(25,13,'vi','Tháng 7 Nên Đi Đâu, Chơi Gì? Gợi Ý Những Điểm Đến Hấp Dẫn Trong Nước & Quốc Tế','thang-7-nen-i-au-choi-gi-goi-y-nhung-iem-en-hap-dan-trong-nuoc-quoc-te','Tháng 7 là mùa cao điểm du lịch hè. Nên đi đâu chơi gì trong tháng 7? Gợi ý những điểm đến hấp dẫn trong nước và quốc tế: biển đẹp, lễ hội sôi động, du lịch châu Âu mùa hè...','<h3> </h3><h2>ThÃ¡ng 7 â Thá»i Äiá»m lÃ½ tÆ°á»ng Äá» du lá»ch hÃ¨</h2><p> </p><p>ThÃ¡ng 7 váº«n Äang lÃ  mÃ¹a nghá» hÃ¨ cá»§a há»c sinh vÃ  sinh viÃªn, Äáº·c biá»t táº¡i miá»n Báº¯c vÃ  mi