ding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">Author: designtvp</span> <span class=\"dates\" style=\"margin: 0px 1em 5px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">Date of publication: 05-06-2026</span><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><h2 data-end=\"3235\" data-start=\"3156\" style=\"font-family: inherit; line-height: 1.1; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Backpacking vs. Luxury Travel â Two Opposite Yet Fascinating Travel Styles</span></h2><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"3443\" data-start=\"3237\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">In the world of travel, two distinct styles stand out: backpacking and luxury travel. Both have unique appeal, offering memorable journeys tailored to different personalities, preferences, and lifestyles.</p><p data-end=\"3443\" data-start=\"3237\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"3443\" data-start=\"3237\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"3443\" data-start=\"3237\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"3443\" data-start=\"3237\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"3443\" data-start=\"3237\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><h2 data-end=\"3498\" data-start=\"3445\" style=\"font-family: inherit; line-height: 1.1; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Backpacking â Freedom and authentic experiences</span></h2><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"3689\" data-start=\"3499\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Backpacking is for those who crave freedom and flexibility. With just a backpack, travelers embark on journeys by motorbike, bus, or train, enjoying every stop as part of a true adventure.</p><p data-end=\"3689\" data-start=\"3499\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"3943\" data-start=\"3691\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">This style emphasizes exploration beyond the typical tourist mapâremote villages, hidden trails, or small local eateries. It is also a chance to connect with locals, savor authentic street food, and immerse yourself in the daily rhythm of local life.</p><p data-end=\"1488\" data-start=\"1207\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"1488\" data-start=\"1207\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"1488\" data-start=\"1207\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/Tips/04/du_lich_bui.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; width: 769.979px; height: 512.062px;\"></p><p data-end=\"1488\" data-start=\"1207\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"1488\" data-start=\"1207\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"1488\" data-start=\"1207\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><h2 data-end=\"4004\" data-start=\"3945\" style=\"font-family: inherit; line-height: 1.1; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Luxury travel â Comfort, relaxation, and rejuvenation</span></h2><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"4200\" data-start=\"4005\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">In contrast, luxury travel is all about comfort, relaxation, and high-end services. Think 5-star hotels, luxury resorts, fine dining, and well-organized itineraries designed for minimal stress.</p><p data-end=\"4200\" data-start=\"4005\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"4446\" data-start=\"4202\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Luxury travel is not just about indulgenceâit is about restoring energy, finding balance, and enjoying every moment with convenience. It is the ideal choice for couples, families, or anyone seeking privacy and sophistication on their journey.</p><p data-end=\"2085\" data-start=\"1797\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"2085\" data-start=\"1797\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"2085\" data-start=\"1797\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/Tips/04/ahaffh-1749112186016.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; width: 769.979px; height: 513.875px;\"></p><p data-end=\"2085\" data-start=\"1797\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"2085\" data-start=\"1797\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"2085\" data-start=\"1797\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"2085\" data-start=\"1797\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><h2 data-end=\"4479\" data-start=\"4448\" style=\"font-family: inherit; line-height: 1.1; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Each style, its own value</span></h2><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"4778\" data-start=\"4480\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">There is no right or wrong when choosing between backpacking and luxury travel. Backpacking challenges you and offers authentic encounters, while luxury travel nurtures you with relaxation and care. Many travelers even combine both stylesâgoing on adventurous trips as well as indulgent getaways.</p><p data-end=\"4778\" data-start=\"4480\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"4778\" data-start=\"4480\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"4778\" data-start=\"4480\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"4778\" data-start=\"4480\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><h2 data-end=\"4818\" data-start=\"4780\" style=\"font-family: inherit; line-height: 1.1; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Travel your way with Travel Plus</span></h2><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p><p data-end=\"5064\" data-start=\"4819\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Whether you are a backpacker at heart or a luxury traveler, Travel Plus offers the perfect journey. From cultural trekking adventures in the mountains to premium beach resort holidays, every trip is designed to be meaningful and unforgettable.</p><p data-end=\"2816\" data-start=\"2540\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"> </p>','BACKPACKING VS. LUXURY TRAVEL – WHICH TRAVEL STYLE SUITS YOU BEST?','Backpacking offers freedom and authentic experiences, while luxury travel provides comfort and relaxation.','2026-06-05 16:09:28','2026-06-05 16:09:28'),(29,15,'vi','SUN PHUQUOC AIRWAYS CHÍNH THỨC MỞ BÁN VÉ ONLINE – BƯỚC KHỞI ĐẦU CỦA “HÀNG KHÔNG NGHỈ DƯỠNG” TẠI VIỆT NAM','sun-phuquoc-airways-chinh-thuc-mo-ban-ve-online-buoc-khoi-au-cua-hang-khong-nghi-duong-tai-viet-nam','Sáng 15/10, Sun PhuQuoc Airways (SPA) – hãng hàng không mới thuộc Tập đoàn Sun Group – đã chính thức mở bán vé trực tuyến, đánh dấu cột mốc quan trọng trong hành trình gia nhập thị trường hàng không Việt Nam.','<p>ÄÃ¢y lÃ  bÆ°á»c khá»i Äáº§u cho má»t cÃ¡i tÃªn há»©a háº¹n mang Äáº¿n lÃ n giÃ³ má»i trong lÄ©nh vá»±c váº­n chuyá»n hÃ ng khÃ´ng, vá»i Äá»nh hÆ°á»ng káº¿t há»£p giá»¯a mÃ´ hÃ¬nh hÃ ng khÃ´ng truyá»n thá»ng vÃ  âhÃ ng khÃ´ng nghá» dÆ°á»¡ngâ (resort aviation) â má»t khÃ¡i niá»m má»i máº» táº¡i Viá»t Nam nhÆ°ng Äang trá» thÃ nh xu hÆ°á»ng toÃ n cáº§u.</p><h3> </h3><h3> </h3><h3> </h3><h3> </h3><h3> </h3><h3><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Táº§m nhÃ¬n má»i trong ngÃ nh hÃ ng khÃ´ng Viá»t Nam</span></h3><p> </p><p> </p><p>Sun PhuQuoc Airways khÃ´ng chá» ÄÆ¡n thuáº§n lÃ  má»t hÃ£ng bay thÆ°Æ¡ng máº¡i. HÃ£ng ÄÆ°á»£c Äá»nh vá» lÃ  cáº§u ná»i giá»¯a tráº£i nghiá»m di chuyá»n vÃ  nghá» dÆ°á»¡ng cao cáº¥p, táº­p trung vÃ o cÃ¡c Äiá»m Äáº¿n du lá»ch ná»i t