hÃ ng cÃ³ thá» Äáº·t vÃ© mÃ¡y bay, khÃ¡ch sáº¡n, vÃ© vui chÆ¡i, xe ÄÆ°a ÄÃ³n sÃ¢n bayâ¦ chá» trong má»t giao dá»ch â tiáº¿t kiá»m thá»i gian vÃ  tá»i Æ°u chi phÃ­.</p><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/VIETNAM/05/asdasd.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>áº¢nh: Sun PhuQuoc Airways</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><h3><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">CÆ¡ há»i má»i cho ngÃ nh du lá»ch Viá»t Nam</span></h3><p> </p><p> </p><p>Sá»± ra Äá»i cá»§a Sun PhuQuoc Airways khÃ´ng chá» mang Ã½ nghÄ©a thÆ°Æ¡ng máº¡i mÃ  cÃ²n thÃºc Äáº©y du lá»ch Viá»t Nam phÃ¡t triá»n máº¡nh máº½ hÆ¡n, Äáº·c biá»t trong bá»i cáº£nh ngÃ nh hÃ ng khÃ´ng Äang há»i phá»¥c vÃ  lÆ°á»£ng khÃ¡ch du lá»ch ná»i Äá»a tÄng cao.</p><p> </p><p>PhÃº Quá»c â âthiÃªn ÄÆ°á»ng Äáº£o ngá»câ â sáº½ lÃ  Äiá»m khá»i Äáº§u quan trá»ng trong hÃ nh trÃ¬nh chinh phá»¥c báº§u trá»i, trÆ°á»c khi hÃ£ng má» rá»ng Äáº¿n cÃ¡c tuyáº¿n bay ná»i Äá»a vÃ  quá»c táº¿ khÃ¡c.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><h3><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Ká»³ vá»ng vÃ o hÃ nh trÃ¬nh má»i</span></h3><p> </p><p> </p><p>Vá»i ná»n táº£ng vá»¯ng cháº¯c tá»« Sun Group cÃ¹ng chiáº¿n lÆ°á»£c phÃ¡t triá»n bÃ i báº£n, Sun PhuQuoc Airways ÄÆ°á»£c ká»³ vá»ng sáº½ trá» thÃ nh biá»u tÆ°á»£ng má»i cá»§a hÃ ng khÃ´ng Viá»t Nam hiá»n Äáº¡i.</p><p> </p><p>Sá»± kiá»n má» bÃ¡n vÃ© online sÃ¡ng nay chá» lÃ  bÆ°á»c Äáº§u tiÃªn cá»§a hÃ nh trÃ¬nh dÃ i, nÆ¡i má»i chuyáº¿n bay khÃ´ng chá» lÃ  di chuyá»n, mÃ  lÃ  má»t pháº§n cá»§a tráº£i nghiá»m nghá» dÆ°á»¡ng cao cáº¥p.</p><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/VIETNAM/05/530232330_122141779010850776_1000307827571164822_n.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\">áº¢nh: Sun PhuQuoc Airways</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p>Sun PhuQuoc Airways â cáº¥t cÃ¡nh hÃ nh trÃ¬nh má»i, ÄÆ°a giáº¥c mÆ¡ bay Viá»t Nam vÆ°Æ¡n xa.</p>','SUN PHUQUOC AIRWAYS CHÍNH THỨC MỞ BÁN VÉ ONLINE – BƯỚC KHỞI ĐẦU CỦA “HÀNG KHÔNG NGHỈ DƯỠNG” TẠI VIỆT NAM','Sáng 15/10, Sun PhuQuoc Airways (SPA) – hãng hàng không mới thuộc Tập đoàn Sun Group – đã chính thức mở bán vé trực tuyến, đánh dấu cột mốc quan trọng trong hành trình gia nhập thị trường hàng không Việt Nam.','2026-06-05 16:40:43','2026-06-05 16:40:43'),(30,15,'en','SUN PHUQUOC AIRWAYS OFFICIALLY LAUNCHES ONLINE TICKET SALES – MARKING THE BEGINNING OF “RESORT AVIATION” IN VIETNAM','sun-phuquoc-airways-officially-launches-online-ticket-sales-marking-the-beginning-of-resort-aviation-in-vietnam','The morning of October 15th, Sun PhuQuoc Airways (SPA) – a new airline founded by Sun Group – officially opened online ticket sales, marking its debut in Vietnam’s aviation market.','<p> </p><p>The launch signifies the arrival of a brand-new name that promises to bring a fresh breeze to Vietnamâs skies, combining traditional aviation models with âresort aviationâ â a concept that merges air travel and high-end tourism experiences.</p><h3> </h3><h3> </h3><h3> </h3><h3> </h3><h3> </h3><h3> </h3><h3><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">A new vision for Vietnamâs aviation industry</span></h3><p> </p><p> </p><p>Sun PhuQuoc Airways positions itself as a bridge between travel and luxury relaxation, focusing on Vietnamâs top destinations such as Phu Quoc, Da Nang, Sa Pa, and Ha Long, where Sun Group has developed world-class resort complexes.</p><p> </p><p>The airline aims to enhance both domestic and international travel experiences, providing flights that are not only safe and punctual but also filled with the spirit of leisure and comfort.</p><p> </p><h3> </h3><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/VIETNAM/05/sun-world-ba-na-hills-10.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"></p><h3> </h3><h3> </h3><h3> </h3><h3> </h3><h3> </h3><h3> </h3><h3><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Seamless online booking experience</span></h3><p> </p><p> </p><p>With online ticketing now available, passengers can easily access the official Sun PhuQuoc Airways website to select flights, schedules, seat classes, and payment methods in just a few clicks.</p><p><br>The modern, user-friendly interface supports multiple languages, ensuring smooth navigation for both local and international travelers.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><h3> </h3><h3><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Resort aviation â redefining flight experiences</span></h3><p> </p><p> </p><p>What sets Sun PhuQuoc Airways apart is its integration of air travel and resort-style hospitality.</p><p><br>Thanks to Sun Groupâs extensive tourism ecosystem, the airline will soon offer exclusive travel packages (flight + resort combo), allowing passengers to enjoy a seamless vacation from takeoff to landing.</p><p> </p><p>Travelers can conveniently book flights, hotels, theme park tickets, and airport transfers all in one transaction, saving both time and cost.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/VIETNAM/05/asdasd.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>Source: Sun PhuQuoc Airways</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><h3><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">A promising boost for Vietnamâs tourism industry</span></h3><p> </p><p> </p><p>The debut of Sun PhuQuoc Airways is not just a commercial milestone â itâs also a strategic push for Vietnamâs tourism growth, especially as both domestic and international travel continue to rebound.</p><p> </p><p>Phu Quoc â the âPearl Islandâ â will be the airlineâs first key destination, before expanding to other domestic and international routes in the near future.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><h3><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Looking ahead</span></h3><p> </p><p> </p><p>Backed by Sun Groupâs strong foundation and vision, Sun PhuQuoc Airways is expected to become a new icon of modern Vietnamese aviation.</p><p> </p><p>The online ticket launch is just the first step in a long journey, where every flight is not only a mode of transport but a gateway to an elevated travel experience.</p><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://travelplusvn.com/public/uploads/images/POST/VIETNAM/05/530232330_122141779010850776_1000307827571164822_n.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>Source: Sun PhuQuoc Airways</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p><span data-end=\"5902\" data-start=\"5830\" style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Sun PhuQuoc Airways â where Vietnamâs new journey in the sky begins.</span></p>','SUN PHUQUOC AIRWAYS OFFICIALLY LAUNCHES ONLINE TICKET SALES – MARKING THE BEGINNING OF “RESORT AVIATION” IN VIETNAM','The morning of October 15th, Sun PhuQuoc Airways (SPA) – a new airline founded by Sun Group – officially opened online ticket sales, marking its debut in Vietnam’s aviation market.','2026-06-05 16:40:43','2026-06-05 16:40:43');
